-- Gold One to Buy Grootvlei Mine in South Africa, BusinessDay Says
-- B y   H i l t o n   S h o n e
-- 2012-03-15T05:23:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/gold-one-to-buy-grootvlei-mine-in-south-africa-businessday-says.html
Australian mining company  Gold One
International Ltd. (GDO)  is the likely buyer of the Grootvlei gold
mine in  South Africa , Business Day reported without saying where
it got the information.  Gold One owns the nearby Modder East mine, the
Johannesburg-based daily said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hilton Shone in Johannesburg at 
 hshone@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
